    <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Relics (Refrence)" hidden="false" id="81b3-1ebe-3f72-c7bf">
      <categoryLinks>
        <categoryLink targetId="9cd6-0442-3f35-6b52" id="f048-e4ad-4be8-0d55" primary="true" name="Configuration"/>
      </categoryLinks>
      <constraints>
        <constraint type="max" value="1" field="selections" scope="force" shared="true" id="6ea7-4439-5ad4-86a1" includeChildSelections="false"/>
      </constraints>
      <profiles>
        <profile name="1. Blood Moon of Khaine" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="6be5-4d96-d9ca-1370">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">For each attack this unit makes, reroll a Hit Roll and Wound Roll of 1 for that attack. Additionally, after this unit’s Attacks step, roll Strands of Fate X where X is equal to the number of Health enemy units lost this turn.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="2. Webway Network" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="4f48-1df1-4fd2-d115">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After this unit is Activated, you may remove it from the battlefield and place it into reserves. Then, you may Deploy it at least 3D6” away from enemy units.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="3. Farseer Spirit Stone" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="a73b-cff7-f2ed-f0e7">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">This unit gains Psyker 3.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="5. Rune of the Bladestorm" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="428e-170c-f3ba-f8ae">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">For each ML attack this unit makes, a Hit Roll of 5+ for that attack causes an additional hit.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="4. Faolchu’s Wing" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="9567-4b7f-ec24-af3d">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After this unit finishes its Attacks step, it may make a March.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="6. Exarch Spirit Stone" typeId="9b56-9768-f88b-14ac" typeName="Relics" hidden="false" id="4192-00a1-633b-7b44">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description" typeId="becf-f398-aed2-688b">After this unit&apos;s End step, if this turn was not your second turn in a row, take another turn. During that turn, if your active unit has an Aspect, X ability, for each attack made by that unit, a Hit Roll of 6 for that attack causes an additional hit.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
    </selectionEntry>
