          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Psychic Power" typeId="9060-973c-99e9-75b4">After this unit makes a Psychic Test, if that Psychic Test had two or more dice with the same result, each enemy unit on the battlefield gains Fatal Thread until the End of the next turn.</characteristic>
