          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Psychic Power" typeId="9060-973c-99e9-75b4">After this unit makes a Psychic Test, if that Psychic Test has two or more dice with the same result, select any friendly unit within 24” of this unit with Wraithbone. The selected unit Heals D3+1.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
