              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After you Activate this unit, select one of the following abilities. until the end step, this unit gains the selected ability;


Surviving Sibling: Eachog this unit&apos;s weapons WS is improved by 1.


Twin&apos;s Essence: That unit&apos;s M is improved by 4&quot;.</characteristic>
