              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit finishes a March, if each of its models is 12” or more from where it started this turn, this unit gains the following ability until the next time it Activates:


Speeding Blur: For each attack that targets this unit, the Hit Roll for that attack is worsened by 1.</characteristic>
              </characteristics>
