              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description" typeId="14c0-3a47-fe6d-6563">Once per battle, after this unit Activates or an enemy unit finishes a March within 16” of this unit, you may ‘dissipate the energy field’. If you do, this unit’s Sv changes to 4+. Then, each enemy unit within 12” of and visible to this unit suffers D3+1 Suppression.</characteristic>
