              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">If this unit would March, you may instead use ‘flickerjump’. If you do, you may remove this unit from the battlefield and place it into reserves. Then, Deploy it anywhere in the battlefield outside of the engagement range of enemy units. If you do, roll a D6 for each model in this unit and for each 1, this unit suffers 2 SW.</characteristic>
