              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit finishes a March, if that move ended at least 16” away from where it started, until the end of the battle round, for each attack that targets this unit, the Hit Roll for that attack is worsened by 1.</characteristic>
